## 2. Tools & Frameworks

| Concern | Choice | Rationale |
|---|---|---|
| **AI Agent Orchestration** | **Mastra** (TypeScript-native) | Already in use; batteries-included: agent loop, tool calling, memory, HITL suspend/resume, guardrail processors, observability, Mastra Studio local UI |
| **LLM** | **Google Gemini 2.0 Flash** | Best free-tier LLM with robust tool-use/function calling support and a massive 1M context window. Perfect for Mastra workflows. |
| **Tool Schema Validation** | **Zod** (via Mastra `createTool`) | Compile-time + runtime type safety on all tool inputs/outputs; enforces ProposedDiff shape |
| **Frontend** | **Next.js 14** (App Router) | Existing vendor portal stack; API routes serve as the BFF/Gateway layer; SSE streaming built-in |
| **Styling** | **Vanilla CSS** (CSS Modules + global variables) | Maximum control; glassmorphism, dark-mode tokens, micro-animations |
| **Database** | **PostgreSQL** | Relational integrity for audit log + mock schema; Mastra's memory adapter is PostgreSQL-native |
| **ORM** | **Prisma** | Type-safe query builder; model-level KYC column exclusion via select views |
| **Session / Cache** | **Redis** (via Mastra memory storage + Upstash adapter) | Mastra thread store for conversation history; in-flight diff storage; fast per-vendor rate-limit counters |
| **Package Manager / Monorepo** | **pnpm + Turborepo** | Fast installs; workspace-aware build pipeline |
| **Testing** | **Vitest** (unit/integration) + **Playwright** (E2E) | Fast TS-native test runner; Playwright for full chat panel flows |
| **Observability** | **Mastra built-in tracing + OpenTelemetry** | Per-turn traces, tool latency, token cost; ships with Mastra out of the box |

